short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Provides command prompt-like navigation of prompt history in ChatGPT.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
ChatGPT Navigation is a simple browser extension designed to enhance your interaction with ChatGPT. Have you ever had a great conversation with ChatGPT and wished you could save the questions for reference or later review? Now you can!

Primary Features:

Up and Down Arrow keys: Go through the history of your questions asked since installation
F7 key: Lists all your questions in the text field.

Update 1.1.2:
Change multi-line comparison for cases of slow page load.

Update 1.1.1:
Change for multi-line text, the caret needs to be at the text beginning for up arrow and text end for down arrow to go through history.
